 traffic delays. Everything seemed terrible about Monday, even the governor had gotten a cold. ","class":"","id":"HK4H7qU7HP4c","block":"text","name":"hOfr"}],"background":"","id":"ZHjdIIYx","block":"group","name":"jstG"},{"marker":"","class":"grid grid-cols-2 gap-2","content":[{"text":"The cityâ€™s favorite football team had lost. They were out of the Super Bowl run-up. There was nothing to celebrate. There would be nothing to cheer up the <b>citizens</b> with that terrible loss. ","class":"","id":"HK4H7qU7HP4cPgyO","block":"text","name":"Pl02"},{"marker":"","class":"flex justify-center items-center ","content":[{"file":"files/img04.jpg","class":"mask mask-squircle","id":"Ts9iqHDGUKJT","block":"image","name":"mdkh"}],"background":"","id":"AAKq4J0AgrGV","block":"group","name":"PjjE"}],"background":"","id":"Kz1eCBZz","block":"group","name":"qauZ"},{"marker":"","class":"grid grid-cols-2 gap-2","content":[{"marker":"","class":"flex justify-center items-center ","content":[{"file":"files/img03.jpg","class":"mask mask-squircle","id":"Ts9iqHDGUKJTgHAS","block":"image","name":"vUEJ"}],"background":"","id":"AAKq4J0AgrGVF0au","block":"group","name":"Dgwl"},{"text":"A 1000 year old sequoia tree had fallen during a storm! Could this day have gotten any worse? Local <b>shopkeepers</b> had angry customers all day. A receptionist, an electrician and even an actor all agreed on having a terrible day. This was definitely the worst day ever for the city. ","class":"","id":"HK4H7qU7HP4cPgyOAWZX","block":"text","name":"6uUC"}],"background":"","id":"irrvdr83","block":"group","name":"ULx7"}],"background":"","id":"jk4C","block":"group","name":"kMiD","hidden":false}],"background":"","name":"4Cs6","hidden":false},{"symbol":"FinalizeGroup"}],"id":""}]},"end":{"buttons":{"restart":false},"content":[{"symbol":"finishedAll"}]},"symbols":{"finishedAll":{"class":"w-full","content":[{"block":"group","class":"bg-slate-100 rounded p-5 text-center w-full","content":[{"block":"text","text":"Congratul